desc:
The possible states of a PrimaryPointerGestureRecognizer.

The recognizer advances from ready to possible when it starts tracking a primary pointer. When the primary pointer is resolved in the gesture arena (either accepted or rejected), the recognizers advances to defunct. Once the recognizer has stopped tracking any remaining pointers, the recognizer returns to ready.
name: gestures.GestureRecognizerState

props.desc:
A constant List of the values in this enum, in order of their declaration.

const List<GestureRecognizerState>
props.name: defunct
